parameters.name: If-Match
parameters.description: If the ETag specified in a request matches the ETag value of the object, OSS transmits the object and returns 200 OK. If the ETag specified in a request does not match the ETag value of the object, OSS returns 412 Precondition Failed.

parameters.name: X-Fc-Account-Id
parameters.description: The ID of your Alibaba Cloud account.

parameters.name: X-Fc-Date
parameters.description: The time when the function is invoked. The value is in the **EEE,d MMM yyyy HH:mm:ss GMT** format.

parameters.name: X-Fc-Trace-Id
parameters.description: The trace ID, which is the unique identifier of a trace.

parameters.name: qualifier
parameters.description: The service alias or LATEST. Versions are not supported.
